constraint: The date shall contain two hyphens.
If there is at least one hyphen, the part before the hyphen shall be a number between 0 and 2025.
If there are at least two hyphens, the part after the first hyphen but before the second hyphen shall be a number between 1 and 12.
result: (=> (>= (str.count s "-") 2) (and (>= (str.to.int (str.substr s (str.indexof s "-") (str.indexof s "-" (str.indexof s "-" 1) + 1))) 1) (<= (str.to.int (str.substr s (str.indexof s "-") (str.indexof s "-" (str.indexof s "-" 1) + 1))) 12)))

constraint: If there are at least two hyphen, The part after the second hyphen shall be a number between 1 and 31.
result: (=> (>= (str.count s "-") 2) (and (>= (str.to.int (str.substr s (str.indexof s "-" (str.indexof s "-" 1) + 1) (str.length s))) 1) (<= (str.to.int (str.substr s (str.indexof s "-" (str.indexof s "-" 1) + 1) (str.length s))) 31)))
